name, age, height (cm), weight (kg)
Jody, 5, 430, 620
Gladys, 10, 420, 590
Marian, 2, 310, 410
Donna, 9, 440, 650

(A) Jody
(B) Gladys
(C) Marian
(D) Donna
(E) Louise

Output final answer with the format <<<answer>>>.
